\begin{verbatim}
Dataset164
\end{verbatim}
A struct containing UFF Dataset 164 metadata.

\textbf{Fields}

\begin{itemize}
\item \texttt{type::Symbol}: Data set type


\item \texttt{units::Int}: Units code


\item \texttt{description::String}: Units description


\item \texttt{temperature\_mode::Int}: Temperature mode


\item \texttt{conversion\_factor::Vector\{Float64\}}: Units factors for converting to SI units

\end{itemize}
